data.description: MOVE IN READY!   Over 1800 SF in the heart of Fraser! Large open kitchen with granite countertops, an island, and a nook open to great room with gas fireplace with mantel and tile surround. Attention to detail with wainscoting throughout the first floor and into the den with French doors. Three bedrooms on the second floor and a master suite with a bathroom and walk-in closet. The home sits on approx. 0.40 acres for you to enjoy and make your new home.  BATVAM
